animeTitle: My Senior Brother is Too Extraordinary
otherNames: My Senior Brother is Too Extraordinary, My Senior Brother is So Outrageous, 我家大师兄太逆天了, 我家大师兄太逆天了 动态漫画
synopsis: Protagonist Zhang Yi suddenly awakens a system, and the first task the system assigns him is to confess his feelings to his cold and aloof master! Is this system trying to get him killed? What’s that? Success will reward him with becoming a saint? Well, it looks like he has no choice but to give it a shot!
